
Named after the notorious Nigerian Advance Fee Fraud (419) scams. 

This application is a simple “Scambaiting” website that enables a connected webcam and takes a stream of vid caps.
If you are lucky these caps will be of your scammer ;) 

“Scambaiting” is becoming a pseudo sport:
http://www.419baiter.com
http://www.419eater.com

Australian gov information:
http://www.scamwatch.gov.au/content/index.phtml/itemId/694299

Please remember you are dealing with criminals and do so at your own risk.

Have Fun! :)

